  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.poster.avif?t=1706736192\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.webm?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.mp4?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Galactic Breakout</strong> is a modern interpretation of the classic Arkanoid, where you need to break different types of blocks with the <strong>paddle</strong> - your best friend.<br><br>Each of the 75 levels has been thoroughly created by hand and the difficulty will gradually increase with each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>3 acts with 25 levels in each</strong><br></li><li> <strong>10 unique power-ups</strong> - with 3 ultimate ones<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/00bb1eb13ccdeda443117dff72e68d83.avif?t=1706736192\" width=380 height=154 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>10 unique and challenging debuffs</strong> - some can easily reduce your score points<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/5de95b8e6680c0ce9c4c504785aff568.avif?t=1706736192\" width=380 height=150 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>Various visual effects for different types of blocks</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.poster.avif?t=1706736192\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.webm?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.mp4?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Custom and <u>Deterministic</u> paddle physics</strong> - control your ball movement as you wish<br></li><li> <strong>Full gamepad support</strong> - use your gamepad to control your paddle and navigate through the UI. You don't need a mouse or keyboard<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/5e976f515d3714bdef0332d86ee586ad.avif?t=1706736192\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>Steam achievements</strong> - 15+ various game achievements to encourage you in your journey</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.poster.avif?t=1706736192\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.webm?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/133e69c0520b08b35fec329632cdf5c4.mp4?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Galactic Breakout</strong> is a modern interpretation of the classic Arkanoid, where you need to break different types of blocks with the <strong>paddle</strong> - your best friend.<br><br>Each of the 75 levels has been thoroughly created by hand and the difficulty will gradually increase with each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>3 acts with 25 levels in each</strong><br></li><li> <strong>10 unique power-ups</strong> - with 3 ultimate ones<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/00bb1eb13ccdeda443117dff72e68d83.avif?t=1706736192\" width=380 height=154 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>10 unique and challenging debuffs</strong> - some can easily reduce your score points<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/5de95b8e6680c0ce9c4c504785aff568.avif?t=1706736192\" width=380 height=150 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>Various visual effects for different types of blocks</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.poster.avif?t=1706736192\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.webm?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/c77b078ca9fc89191c6e9b3e6f3f5a23.mp4?t=1706736192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Custom and <u>Deterministic</u> paddle physics</strong> - control your ball movement as you wish<br></li><li> <strong>Full gamepad support</strong> - use your gamepad to control your paddle and navigate through the UI. You don't need a mouse or keyboard<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666260/extras/5e976f515d3714bdef0332d86ee586ad.avif?t=1706736192\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br></li><li> <strong>Steam achievements</strong> - 15+ various game achievements to encourage you in your journey</li></ul>",
